{
    "version": 6,
    "bundle": "O2FPMY5JL62ETD6YS4UCL3UNDZEQBTKK",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041049005",
    "title": "浮世に生きりゃ取沙汰だらけ",
    "enTitle": "A Harsh World Full of Uncertainty",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日、仕事をしていると……\nナカヤマフェスタの担任がトレーナー室にやってきた。",
            "enText": "One day, while I was working... Nakayama Festa's homeroom teacher came to the trainer's office.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 799189540785886237,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "担任の教師",
            "enName": "Homeroom Teacher",
            "jpText": "そうですか……ナカヤマさん、ここにも来ていないんですね。\nお仕事中お騒がせしてすみません。",
            "enText": "I see... Nakayama isn't here either. Sorry for bothering you while you were in the middle of something.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 257,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "pathId": -5493953547168626083,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "担任の教師",
            "enName": "Homeroom Teacher",
            "jpText": "はあ、困ったわ……今週中に課題を出してもらわないと、\n成績がつけられないのに……。",
            "enText": "Haaah, I'm in trouble... I need to get her completed assignment by the end of the week so I can grade it...",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 231,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "さ、捜すの手伝います……！！",
                    "enText": "I-I'll help you find her!\n",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -86635207425733950,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマの同級生A",
            "enName": "Nakayama's Classmate A",
            "jpText": "ナカヤマさんの居場所？　さあ……あの子と全然交流なくて……。",
            "enText": "Where's Nakayama? Who knows. I've never talked to her.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 167,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "pathId": -6647647420345310686,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマの同級生B",
            "enName": "Nakayama's Classmate B",
            "jpText": "ナカヤマさん、なんかちょっと近寄りがたいっていうか。\nほら、この前も補導されたって聞いたし……。",
            "enText": "Nakayama's always seemed a bit unapproachable. Y'know, I heard that he was arrested the other day.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 275,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "補導……？",
                    "enText": "Arrested…?\n",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2339773210208895616,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマの同級生B",
            "enName": "Nakayama's Classmate B",
            "jpText": "あ、はい……ランニング中の友だちが見たらしいんですけど、\n河川敷で、何か警察の人と言い争ってたって……。",
            "enText": "Oh, yeah… while a friend of mine was on a run, she saw Nakayama arguing with an officer…",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 288,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 90,
                    "pathId": 557115069331251624
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -8687850076733452648
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2226023180011630026,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ガラの悪そうなウマ娘",
            "enName": "Rough-Looking Umamusume",
            "jpText": "はあ……知るわけないっしょ。あいつがどこいるかなんて。\nったく、どいつもこいつもナカヤマナカヤマってさあ。",
            "enText": "Huh? How should I know? I got no clue where she is. Seriously, it's all just Nakayama this, Nakayama that.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 282,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "え、俺以外に誰か彼女を……？",
                    "enText": "Eh? Who else besides me is…?\n",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "え、私以外に誰か彼女を……？",
                    "enText": "Eh? Who else besides me is…?\n",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": -499296334757516170
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3828605329782862283,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ガラの悪そうな男子",
            "enName": "Rough-Looking Boy",
            "jpText": "この前もあいつのこと捜してるって奴が来てよお。\nは、どうせあんたも、ナカヤマに一杯食わされたクチだろ？",
            "enText": "The other day, some other guys came by looking for her. You were one of the ones Nakayama made a fool of, weren't you?",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 259,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "！？その話、詳しく教えてくれ……！",
                    "enText": "…? Can you tell me more?\n",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "！？その話、詳しく教えて……！",
                    "enText": "…? Can you tell me more?\n",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1166210010365719557,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ガラの悪そうなウマ娘",
            "enName": "Rough-Looking Umamusume",
            "jpText": "ん？　あんたはあのトラブル絡みじゃないのか。\nほら、ナカヤマが――",
            "enText": "Hm? I assumed you were involved in that mess. Y'see, apparently…",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 196,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "pathId": 7023339201650997288,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ガラの悪そうなウマ娘",
            "enName": "Rough-Looking Umamusume",
            "jpText": "ポーカーにイカサマ仕込んで、バカ勝ちしたって話。\nで、ダマされた奴らに追われてるんだってさ。",
            "enText": "Nakayama cheated during a poker game and won big. Now, she's being chased down by the people she cheated.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 240,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 283,
                    "pathId": 2372409958310020229
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -7527147711731012512
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -755528097267766205,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ガラの悪そうなウマ娘",
            "enName": "Rough-Looking Umamusume",
            "jpText": "連中、目の色変えてそこら中捜し回ってるぜ。\nあーあー、どうなっちまうのかねえ、あいつ。",
            "enText": "They're looking all over the place looking for her. Aaah, I wonder how she'll end up.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 265,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（おかしい。そんなはずは……）",
                    "enText": "(That's weird… it can't be…)\n",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 26,
                    "pathId": 7345861502476733707
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2580690145847002922,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その後も噂を頼りにいろいろな場所を捜しまわったものの、\nナカヤマフェスタの行方は依然として知れない。",
            "enText": "After that, I followed rumors to various different places, but Nakayama Festa's whereabouts remained unknown.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 5283881779364315605,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "代わりに知ったのは、ナカヤマフェスタに関する\nよからぬ噂だった。彼女がそんなことをするはずは――",
            "enText": "What I got instead was plenty of unsavory gossip about things Nakayama Festa would never do.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "あ、ナカヤマ！！",
                    "enText": "Ah, Nakayama!\n",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -1618070653129478016
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2572294688620823043,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "ん……？　ああ、トレーナーか。\nなんだか青い顔してんなァ？",
            "enText": "Hmm...? Oh, trainer? You look blue in the face.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 228,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いや、実は……",
                    "enText": "Well, actually...\n",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 125,
                    "pathId": -5310236606455953928
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 8351503285358399334
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1719603266851164007,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ナカヤマフェスタに事のあらましを話す。\n課題のことを教えるため、彼女を捜し始めたこと、そして――",
            "enText": "I told Nakayama Festa the whole story. How I'd started looking for her due to the assignment, but then—",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 24,
                    "pathId": 5263459354085127349
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2396148547576490394,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "警察からの補導に、勝負でのイカサマ――学園内外に、\n彼女に関する様々な噂が飛び交っていることを。",
            "enText": "I'd learned rumors about her from both in out of school, from cheating in games to getting in trouble with the police.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 107,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -6241444302345961436,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "ハハハハッ……知らねえ間に随分おもしれえ話が\n広まってるじゃねえか。",
            "enText": "Hahaha… I didn't even know there were such interesting stories being thrown around.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 242,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 142,
                    "pathId": 8370333172995948080
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 6529885988324177899
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1834359199021121841,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "んなもん、全部デタラメだ。イカサマしてバカ勝ちだァ？\nハン、くだらねえ。んなことしても、何もヒリつかねえだろうが。",
            "enText": "They're nonsense. Cheating to win big? Hah, that's bullshit. I wonder if it would even light up anything in me.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 412,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 156,
                    "pathId": -424726606334671114
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 319,
                    "pathId": -6353816735899137995
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4244190328358529891,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "……ま、つまんねえ噂撒いてんのは、おおかた私に何かの\n勝負で負けた連中だ。それだけ恨み妬み買ってるってワケだ。",
            "enText": "…The people who are spreading that sort of crap are the same ones who've lost some kind of competition to me. That's how much they resent and envy me.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 386,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 438,
                    "pathId": -3598989079935199462
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 8723285547610134318
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2650702345106901598,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "たしかに、勝負の世界に生きる彼女には敵も多そうだ。\nだが、怖気づいている場合ではない。彼女のトレーナーとして――",
            "enText": "Indeed, she seems to have many enemies in the world of competition. But this is no time to be intimidated. As her trainer—",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "何かあったら俺が君を守る",
                    "enText": "If anything happens, I'll protect you.",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "何かあったら私が貴方を守る",
                    "enText": "If anything happens, I'll protect you.",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 260,
                    "pathId": -2243180466199937710
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8042412423216954889,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "へぇ……？　随分威勢がいいねえ。\nそういうアンタも、とばっちり食らうかもしんねえぞ？",
            "enText": "Eh…? You're brash, aren't you? You might get in trouble too, you know?",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 320,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "どんな目に遭っても、君を支えてみせる",
                    "enText": "No matter what anyone says, I'll stand by you.",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "どんな目に遭っても、貴方を支えてみせる",
                    "enText": "No matter what anyone says, I'll stand by you.",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 261,
                    "pathId": 7288714923519334682
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": -7465599982750782274
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4173410682160636487,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "へえ、どんな目にも、ねぇ。\n……ククッ……口ではどうとでも言えるな。",
            "enText": "No matter what anyone thinks, eh? Keheh… easier said than done.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 370,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 305,
                    "pathId": 4665367861084008078
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 25,
                    "pathId": -3638423810367748497
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5620106315262961997,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "まァ、そうイキるなよ。\nアンタは私の“トレーナー”だろ。",
            "enText": "Don't get so smug. You are my trainer.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 229,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 216,
                    "pathId": 335364879639260533
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1594788960351429376,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "私にとって、レースこそが生きる場所。\nその機会をフイにしちまうようなドジは踏まねえ。",
            "enText": "For me, racing is why I live. I won't make the mistake of screwing up that opportunity.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 251,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 263,
                    "pathId": -7481999806706772940
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1645186962295089729,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "トレーナーのアンタは、それだけ知ってりゃ十分だ。\nなァ、そうだろ？",
            "enText": "That's all you need to know as my trainer, yeah?",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 205,
            "voiceIdx": 18,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": 8040494946376609662
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 7910684926742698613
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6019908305274723552,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ナカヤマフェスタ",
            "enName": "Nakayama Festa",
            "jpText": "ま、気楽にいこうぜ、お互いによ。",
            "enText": "Well then, both of us should just take it easy.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 123,
            "voiceIdx": 19,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -666848258792529735
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -11605988298974391
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -548199348681891713,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ナカヤマフェスタのことを信じる気持ちは変わらない。だが――\nもっと彼女のことを知らなければ――そう痛感した1日だった。",
            "enText": "I will never change my mind about Nakayama Festa. However, I still felt as if I needed to learn more about her.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -7429376302722092480
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8093905036828680271,
            "blockIdx": 27
        }
    ],
